Import

Endpoint:https://dev1.immosurance.net/yiiapp/backend/web

CSV/XLS import

Import Data (CSV/XLS)

POST
https://dev1.immosurance.net/yiiapp/backend/web
/import/import-data

API to import data of specific model.

Import Data (CSV/XLS) › Headers

  • X-Api-Keystring · required

    The X-Api-Key header is used to authenticate with your API key.

Import Data (CSV/XLS) › Request Body

  • modelNamestring · required

    Name of model whose data is going to be imported.
    Accepted values: 'property', 'client', 'dossier'

  • filestring · required

    Accepted formats: 'csv', 'xls', 'xlsx'.
    Make sure file contains header and at least one row.

Import Data (CSV/XLS) › Responses

Successful import request

  • importIdstring · required

    Unique ID to get import status

  • estimated_timestring

    Estimated time to complete import

POST /import/import-data

Check Import Status

GET
https://dev1.immosurance.net/yiiapp/backend/web
/import/import-status

Check the progress and current state of an import by its ID.

Check Import Status › query Parameters

  • importIdstring · required

    The ID of the import job

Check Import Status › Headers

  • X-Api-Keystring · required

    The X-Api-Key header is used to authenticate with your API key.

Check Import Status › Responses

Successful import operation

  • successboolean · required

    Indicates if the import request was successful

  • dataobject · required
